[Name] GtkSourceView
[Summary] A text widget with syntax highlighting and other features of a source code editor
[Description] GtkSourceView is a portable C library that extends the standard GTK+ framework for multiline text editing with support for configurable syntax highlighting, unlimited undo/redo, UTF-8 compliant caseless searching, printing and other features typical of a source code editor.
[License] GNU General Public License version 2, GNU Lesser General Public License version 2.1
[Homepage] https://projects.gnome.org/gtksourceview/
